data.description: Excellent Investment Opportunity! Classic waterfront home in quiet Big Torch Key. This home features 2 bedrooms, two bathrooms and a spacious open living/dining/kitchen area. Water from a 12k gallon cistern with a reverse osmosis system. City water is available and the home is connected to sewer. This home is being sold as a life estate. The homeowner will remain in place after purchase of the home. Details will be negotiated with the right buyer. Great boating from the 50 foot wide canal with little traffic. Come enjoy the peacefulness  and privacy you are looking for in the Keys.
